26.1.3. PDF: Businesses - Renewal Application

These merges will be accessible from a Business Application, as well as from the main menu.

  


Automatically Creating Draft Applications

We will have an annual process that will create new applications for all businesses that are active and filed an application last year. In practice, new businesses will not be in the system unless FB has an application.

  


This logic works because self-filing businesses will not have any application in the system.

  


The new application will:

  * Complete Year 2/2 applications with the specified amount, following a Year 1/2 application
  * Create Year 1/2 applications following a Year 2/2 application
  * Create Single-Year applications following a Single-Year Application



  


It will also default the application type (Pre-K/K-12/OSTC) based on the prior application.

  


Generated Application Form

The generated application form will reflect fields such as the multiple-choice Enterprise Type and Entity Type. It will also automatically fill the Contribution Info amount (for Year 2/2) and the application type (Pre-K/K-12/OSTC).

Printing Applications

We will have an option to print all current-year applications that have not yet been sent to the business.
